title: Theotis Beasley Ad Day
description: Theotis just turned Pro but that doesn’t mean he is slowing down one bit. We wrangled him up one Saturday and had him take us to some of his local spots. Theo handled business and got the back side flip for the Ad. Congrats on turning Pro Theo!!!!
